channel.title: My 2 cents
channel.description:
My 1st cent is. People need to stop "making 459 servers" and calling it theirs.
The 459(Proj Anni) that was released, is more of a step back, then a step forward. The only real progress that was done, was by mostly Brown, and thing1 did a few things.
Scully just released without permission, he claims it was leaked, but he was the one who leaked it.
Heres your argument: Dude, its hyperion!
Answer: And..? It doesn't mean it can be written awful and can be unstable.
2nd Cent: Does anyone know how to open a RS formatted file? Idk how to open them..
